Text: Hey. Managed to install. But Your keygen is not working buddy. Any insights?

@qwertyuiop9091

you have to extract from brs1r11a to brs1r11n and then hit the first new brs1r11 and click extract again. Then 2 folders appear "Setup" and "Keygen". I hope i was helpful
